            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "This seems to fix the problem:\r\n```diff\r\ndiff --git a/src/nvim/window.c b/src/nvim/window.c\r\nindex 530cbc0c7..54d06eb62 100644\r\n--- a/src/nvim/window.c\r\n+++ b/src/nvim/window.c\r\n@@ -814,6 +814,7 @@ void win_config_float(win_T *wp, FloatConfig fconfig)\r\n     Error dummy = ERROR_INIT;\r\n     win_T *parent = find_window_by_handle(wp->w_float_config.window, &dummy);\r\n     if (parent) {\r\n+      win_grid_alloc(parent);\r\n       row += parent->w_winrow;\r\n       col += parent->w_wincol;\r\n       ScreenGrid *grid = &parent->w_grid;\r\n```",
